parameters:
Mel: I may just be a substitute for the
Demon Lord, but I'll do my best with
what I can do.

Mel: ...However, if I hadn't returned,
wouldn't the Demon Continent have fallen
into chaos?

Azel: Since there is no royal family
member, the response must have been
delayed.
Claudia: That's a promise I won't say.
Lala: Thank goodness for Mel's return...

Megildin: After defeating Eden, the
turmoil finally settled down.

Megildin: This is all thanks to Lady
Zerachiel. I am grateful for her as the
queen of the Demon Continent.

Zerachiel: Oh no, that's not true! If
everyone hadn't cooperated, we wouldn't
have been able to accomplish anything.

Megildin: You persevered and carried out
what you needed to do. You should be
proud.

Effy: Thank you for everything, Demon
Lord-sama.

Megildin: Former Saint of the Orpheus
Church, huh? You seem lively, which is
good to see.

Megildin: From now on, grasp your own
happiness.

Sachia: It seems that we are currently
hiring adventurers and mercenaries to
strengthen the forces of Varr.

Sachia: It seems that our forces have
grown larger compared to before.

Claudia: Since there is Adamas ore in
the Demon Continent, it seems that our
weapons and armor will be well-equipped.

Rabi: From now on in Logres, we can
expect a battle with the Choir.

Rabi: Even if we take Effy-sama out
first, it's about that Zerachiel.

Rabi: They'll probably involve the
residents out of spite.
Zerachiel: I wonder what I should do...

Rabi: However, I got involved in
something unbelievable.

Sachia: Because Vahl and Logres have
already been attacked.

Mel: If the Star God obtains the Seventh
Curse, they will surely attack us
seriously.

Marnagarm: Seventh Curse -- Is this the
perfected form of the curse by Orpheus?

Marnagarm: To think that the curse
Orpheus sealed away at the cost of his
own life would revive once again...

Lala: You know what kind of power the
Seventh Curse has, don't you, doggie?

Marnagarm: It was because there were
gods back then that even humans could
survive.

Marnagarm: However, in the modern era
where many gods have disappeared, we
cannot resist.

Aries: Originally, the Seventh Curse was
a curse created by Orpheus to end the
war...

Aries: There should have been many
casualties among Eden's forces.

Marnagarm: In the process, we introduced
the Homunculus.

Zerachiel: Are those people from Eden
planning to involve even their allies...

Marnagarm: Yes, Eden is that kind of
god.

Marnagarm: If they can ultimately
dominate the world, they will use any
means necessary.
Azel: A curse that even gods fear...

Zerachiel: In any case, what we do
remains unchanged.

Zerachiel: Remiel, Sariel, Eden... I
won't let things go according to their
plans.

Zerachiel: I will only retrieve Effy
with my own hands.

Rabi: Oh my, I'm getting the shivers of
a warrior!

Rabi: A formidable enemy awaits. As a
martial artist, I can't help but get
excited.
Claudia: Rabi is as lively as ever...
Sachia: But, my anxiety has disappeared.

Lala: In any case, it seems like it
would be better to prepare before
boarding.

Claudia: That's right... I don't know
what awaits us.

Azel: The Demon Lord and the army are
waiting in the sanctuary, so let's head
there once we're ready.

Zerachiel can no longer use Call
Friends. From now on, Pururin can be
freely organized.

Managarm: Do you have business with
Logres?

Managarm: Then, let's begin the
transfer. Close your eyes.
Marnagarm: Shall we return to Logres?

Marnagarm: Then, let's initiate the
transfer. Close your eyes.
Marnagarm: Where should we teleport to?
Head towards the Tree of Dreams
Head to the realm of dreams and illusions

Marnagarm: Alright, let's begin the
teleportation. Close your eyes.

Marnagarm: Alright, let's begin the
teleportation. Close your eyes.

Marnagarm: Alright, let's begin the
teleportation. Close your eyes.

Knight: The small light of destiny
entrusted to you. It has brought forth
great peace.

Knight: Your desperate efforts go beyond
the existence of God and can even create
miracles...

Knight: You have carved your own path
and guided the people with your own
strength.

Zerachiel: I never intended to do
anything grandiose...

Effy: Hehe, it means that I am being
appreciated that much...

Knight: You moved the Demon Lord and
saved the world from crisis.

Knight: Furthermore, even the Star God
Eden was destroyed.
Knight: ...Could it be, are you the God?

Zerachiel: Ahahaha, with my beauty, I
wonder if I can gain more followers.

Effy: If I grow a little more, there
might be a possibility...

Zerachiel: Where do you think you're
looking and saying that!!
